Beijing to Host International Music Festival
BEIJING , September 21 ( Xinhua ) -- The Beijing International Music Festival will be held in the capital city from October 13 to 25 , the Municipal Foreign Cultural Exchange Association , the event 's organizer , announced today .
This festival , the first of its kind , will offer some 20 performances by many musicians from around the world including renouned tenor Jose Carreras .
This musical gala will be held every year , and is expected to become a cultural landmark activity for Beijing .
the organizer said .
